:::'''Lady Vermilion:''' Tweet! I'm not afraid of you... Tweet? Oh, it's not Boss Stone. You really scared me there, tweet.
:::'''Lady Vermilion:''' *Ahem* You don't look familiar, dear customer. Welcome to the Town Hotel, tweet~
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Town Hotel?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_414030304-->
:::'''Lady Vermilion:''' Yes. This is the only hotel in Dreamville... and also my proudest achievement, tweet.
:::'''Lady Vermilion:''' Look at this dreamy dome built from branches, the stone-decorated carved walls, the brilliant corridor paved with mud. How romantic... Wouldn't you love to spend an unforgettable and wonderful night here? Tweet tweet?
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Sure would!
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_414030307-->
::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' Heehee, you are very keen. You're sure to be delighted with this. Tweet!
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Not interested!
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_414030309-->
::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' Hmm, you're so apathetic. But then again... This kind of guest is also really cool, tweet.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Thanks for the invite. I've just stayed the night there.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_414030311-->
::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' Eh? Thank you for your patronage, tweet! We hope Boss Stone didn't keep you up last night... If you're still afraid, I can come and make sure you fall asleep, tweet~
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_414030312-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_414030312-->
:::'''Lady Vermilion:''' It's a real shame. If times were normal, I would definitely entertain you properly, tweet.
:::'''Lady Vermilion:''' But Boss Stone has sent lots of baddies to the hotel recently, and I'm really worried about the little birds going out... It would be amazing if some kind-hearted guest could help me find them, tweet~
:::The origami bird winks its bright eyes at you. You're unsure whether it's flirting with you or it's just the common bird behavior.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Let me help you.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_414030316-->
::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' You're indeed a very good person, tweet! Once all of Boss Stone's baddies scram, I'll definitely show you around Dreamville, tweet!
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Go look for them yourself.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_414030318-->
::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' Eek~ The hotel's so dangerous right now. What if I get caught by Boss Stone? You ought to protect a delicate lady like me, tweet~
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} (Indifferent)
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_414030320-->
::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' Dear guest &mdash; please stop playing the fool, tweet. I really need your help, tweet!
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_414030321-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_414030321-->
